headline: Go Green! Consumers Energy Expands Residential Renewable Energy Options for All Michiganders
summary: Consumers Energy today announced two major milestones in its commitment to renewable energy. Michigan's largest energy provider is expanding its renewable offerings with the launch of "Green Giving", a one-of-a-kind program that allows everyone to contribute to our renewable energy future.
